data.description: The Cali is a spacious ranch Floorplan offering 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths and a 2-car garage. Large kitchen island that overlooks the dining area and the living room creating an open concept living space. This home also has a large Owner's Suite with walk-in shower and a double vanity, large walk-in-closet and linen closet. Stainless Steel Appliances, Window Blinds and Home is Connected, America's Smart Home! Photos used for illustrative purposes and do not depict actual home.
